sentences.english: In late November, Northeast Field Army was ordered into the customs.
sentences.chinese: 月下旬，東北野戰軍奉命入關。

sentences.english: This is a signal of the urgent urgency from Field Army Headquarters.
sentences.chinese: 這是野戰軍首長拍來的十萬火急的電報。

sentences.english: We need the support of the field army when we are in field operations.
sentences.chinese: 打仗的時候我們需要野戰軍的支持。
